{"tid":1813044,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「18區議會入」港共自己都係行人隧道做文宣 我地點解唔可以？","createTime":"2020-01-06T03:34:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-15T09:41:45.000Z","uid":158613,"like":37,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"124fce86f8902809fd99c647f53740e545296233","tid":1813044,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T03:34:48.000Z","msg":"港共自己都係行人隧道做文宣 我地點解唔可以？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LfscZFL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLfscZFL.jpg&h=778acf14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>18區區議會</strong></ins><br />\n每區區議會需在該區人流就多既位置，<strong>安裝正式既連農文宣牆 (情況有如廣告箱)，</strong> <br />\n同時安排保安公司管理。 費用就香港人既錢(公帑)支付。<br />\n<br />\n以上工程，由黃色工程公司負責，當中可請手足full / part time幫手。<br />\n對家用呢重方法玩咗廿幾年，今次到香港人！<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>[不同政見，都可以提交文宣]</strong></ins><br />\n機會平等，所有人都可以將文宣交到當區區議員手上<br />\n佢地會有既定「機制」去分類放上連農<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>我地要好好理用手上 區議會權力同資源</ins></strong><br />\n- 18-1區文宣正式化<br />\n- 擴大及鞏固黃色經濟圈<br />\n- 支援手足 保護手足"},{"pid":"46fa44292aa154a3485a7576a0210b44b54512cd","tid":1813044,"uid":158613,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T03:39:25.000Z","msg":"港共自己都係行人隧道做文宣 我地點解唔可以？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LfscZFL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLfscZFL.jpg&h=778acf14&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1e6eb9ac16543fd3197930242033e4ba2e8321e0","tid":1813044,"uid":202720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T03:41:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e9699f188c1b4ebae7fea9c6427a21fe3c1f57d7","tid":1813044,"uid":228491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T03:44:42.000Z","msg":"推 Gchi"},{"pid":"f64fa24ca3d42592513ba1ddd4a91d13964ce2b9","tid":1813044,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T04:06:40.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"57e70aaee473e1e346d672c49c8a6fe9ab5b8cef","tid":1813044,"uid":14494,"like":0,"disli